      "title": "Yeds Supporters Group to Walk from Boundary Park to Spotland Ahead of Derby",
      "slug": "yeds-supporters-group-to-walk-from-boundary-park-to-spotland-for-fundraiser",
      "excerpt": "The Yeds Supporters Group will walk from Boundary Park to Spotland on August 30 to raise funds for their club ahead of the derby against Rochdale Hornets.",
      "content_html": "<p>A group of supporters from Oldham Athletic, known as the Yeds Supporters Group, are organising a fundraising walk from Boundary Park to Spotland. The event is scheduled for August 30, ahead of the derby match against Rochdale Hornets.</p><p>The initiative aims to raise funds for the club and engage the community in support of their team. Participants will make the journey on foot, demonstrating their commitment to the club.</p><p>This walk is part of a series of activities designed to bolster support and raise financial contributions for the Yeds. The supporters group encourages fans to join in and contribute to the cause.</p>",
